# Build artifacts
/target

# Secrets — NEVER commit these.
# NOTE: .gitignore has no inline comments — text after a pattern on the same
# line becomes part of the pattern, so keep comments on their own lines.
# your real config (may hold account id / OAuth ids)
/config.toml
# RSA private/public keys
*.pem
*.key
private_key*
public_key*

# Local data & logs
/data
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.log

# Tauri desktop build artifacts
/src-tauri/target
/src-tauri/gen
/node_modules

# Public Microsoft code-signing roots — safe to commit despite *.pem above
# (verifies the bundled WebView2 bootstrapper at installer-build time)
!scripts/microsoft-roots.pem
